methods.name: DeserializeIntoIsolate
methods.logic: Deserializes the shared heap data into the current isolate. It checks if the isolate owns its string tables and deserializes the shared heap object cache, string table, and deferred objects. It also rehashes if necessary.

methods.name: DeserializeStringTable
methods.logic: Deserializes the string table from the snapshot.  It reads the size of the string table from the source, then reads each string object, and finally inserts these strings into the isolate's string table.
